Subject: [PATCH] drm/vmwgfx: Create debugfs ttm_resource_manager entry only if
 needed
References: bsc#1218260
Patch-mainline: 6.6.24
Git-commit: 4be9075fec0a639384ed19975634b662bfab938f

commit 4be9075fec0a639384ed19975634b662bfab938f upstream.

The driver creates /sys/kernel/debug/dri/0/mob_ttm even when the
corresponding ttm_resource_manager is not allocated.
This leads to a crash when trying to read from this file.

Add a check to create mob_ttm, system_mob_ttm, and gmr_ttm debug file
only when the corresponding ttm_resource_manager is allocated.

